  coach_language = 'Primary subrole: Double vertical press strength. Score Strength high. Add a small Explosiveness score only when the coach uses crisp concentric intent, low fatigue, and adequate rest; do not reframe this card as a swing, snatch, jump, plyometric, or conditioning station.',
